item.title: Compiling errors
item.dc:creator: @heroisgay heroisgay
item.description:
@heroisgay wrote:

Go to: http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

After you download and install JDK

Make a compile.bat file with:

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_07\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause

In it. Change the “.0_0#” to the value of JDK you have, for example

@echo off Title Compiler "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_10\bin\javac.exe" *.java pause
